description: {"blocks":[{"key":"20rni","text":"Welcome!","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"71hg9","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3v4uc","text":"You have reached the Protocols.io workspace for the University of California, Santa Cruz Chemical Screening Center.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"2hlep","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"9iaie","text":"Please refer to the CSC website for information on training, instrument specifications, rules, contact and visitor information, social media, etc. csc.ucsc.edu.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":146,"length":14}],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":147,"length":12}],"data":{}},{"key":"ab25e","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"link","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"guid":"5D5DA1607CDC11EDB03BF3FE6A89F73F","url":"http://csc.ucsc.edu"}}}}
document: {"blocks":[{"key":"4mlgc","text":"If you see a protocol that you are interested in using, you have 4 options:","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"italic","offset":0,"length":75},{"style":"bold","offset":0,"length":75}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"34fmp","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"6k208","text":"- use the protocol as is without changing it,","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"bj39h","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"5scq9","text":"- make a \"fork\", and then you can change your fork to whatever you want and distribute it to whomever you want,","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"5b7qj","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"skk3","text":"- make a \"version\", and then you will be able to contribute your improvements to the protocol e.g. add pictures, sample data, movies, detailed tips, etc. that everyone would benefit from (this will trigger a request for permission to go to the owner),","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"9fktc","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"eh7pg","text":"- request to be a member of the CSC workspace and get editing privileges for the protocol you want to edit directly.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
